{"tid":2159550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【零售浩劫】英快速時尚巨頭Topshop中環旗艦店即將關門","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:43:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb790e0c380d8448ddef58c88ea336f483e277fd","tid":2159550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L.oMYSYqhOVuOf0pP9ol5g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/b69c451d2fa1810f273680b68998d223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FL.oMYSYqhOVuOf0pP9ol5g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb69c451d2fa1810f273680b68998d223&h=a2c5c332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c07e40b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】英國快速時尚巨頭Topshop在一個月前傳出不再續租位於中環的旗艦店，周日(16日)Topshop正式在其社交平台發文公布「WE'RE CLOSING SOON(關店在即)」，並感謝支持者長久以來的愛護。<br />\n<br />\n在7月上旬，市傳Topshop在今年10月約滿後便關閉座落中環的最後一間香港分店，將撤出香港實體店市場，只維持網上服務。資料顯示，該旗艦店於2013年中開幕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/零售浩劫-英快速時尚巨頭topshop中環旗艦店即將關門-090335703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E6%B5%A9%E5%8A%AB-%E8%8B%B1%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%99%82%E5%B0%9A%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%ADtopshop%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E5%BA%97%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80-090335703.html&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b0431e84\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/零售浩劫-英快速時尚巨頭topshop中環旗艦店即將關門-090335703.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e4eafcd1670b54518ba3e27ed614598d743bf3e","tid":2159550,"uid":361783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"去